title: 148: Is Being An Only Child Better? (AMA) | Ear Biscuits Ep. 148
description:
Rhett & Link answer your questions on everything from games they invented as kids, what they remember most about the Tour of Mythicality, what it's like being an only child and more on this week's Ear Biscuits. 




Listen to Ear Biscuits at: 

Apple Podcasts: applepodcasts.com/earbiscuits

Spotify: spoti.fi/2oIaAwp

Art19: art19.com/shows/ear-biscuits
